{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-list-tsx","path":"/tags/RSS/","result":{"data":{"allMdx":{"nodes":[{"excerpt":"LLM 与 AI 的热潮激活了我对新鲜资讯的渴望，遂重新回想起来了 RSS 阅读器的存在。最开始想要让浏览器包办一切，因为自己总会切换不同的设备，而 Chrome 能同步安装的浏览器拓展，于是试用了知名度最高的 RSS Feed Reader。然而它并不是免费做慈善的，最大的限制是只能保存每个订阅源最新的 50 条内容，超出的部分就啪地一声不见了。对于更新较慢的博客来说，这个限制没有什么影响…","fields":{"slug":"openclaw-with-rss"},"frontmatter":{"banner":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/9ea8515d3cd8c43a7acf24fd2736c24d/90a86/banner.png","srcSet":"/static/9ea8515d3cd8c43a7acf24fd2736c24d/e7e5d/banner.png 658w,\n/static/9ea8515d3cd8c43a7acf24fd2736c24d/c0cda/banner.png 1316w,\n/static/9ea8515d3cd8c43a7acf24fd2736c24d/90a86/banner.png 2632w","sizes":"(min-width: 2632px) 2632px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/9ea8515d3cd8c43a7acf24fd2736c24d/b161b/banner.webp 658w,\n/static/9ea8515d3cd8c43a7acf24fd2736c24d/d66ba/banner.webp 1316w,\n/static/9ea8515d3cd8c43a7acf24fd2736c24d/083a7/banner.webp 2632w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 2632px) 2632px, 100vw"}]},"width":2632,"height":1755}}},"categories":["人工智能"],"tags":["AI","OpenClaw","RSS","FreshRSS","RSSHub"],"title":"AI 时代的 RSS 订阅：基于 OpenClaw 的 FreshRSS 实战","date":"2026-04-08T00:00:00.000Z","updated":"2026-04-21T00:00:00.000Z","timeliness":45}}]}},"pageContext":{"ids":["f4b5b3ed-efe6-5381-bc51-b8352022c145"],"tag":"RSS"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2291570122","2940271172"],"slicesMap":{}}